raci Watch Change — Auto Color Demo
// No `roles` directive, no `| color: …` on phases or roles.
// Renderer auto-rotates marker-safe accents (orange / green / cyan)
// for the column tints and phase bars.

[Eight Bells]
  Wake the relief
    Bos: A R
    Cook: I
  Trim the lamps
    Lamp: A R
    Bos: I
  Bring up coffee
    Cook: A R
    Steward: I

[Four Bells]
  Stand the wheel
    Helm: A R
    Nav: C
  Heave the log
    Helm: A
    Mate: R
    Crew: I
  Strike eight bells
    Bos: A R
    Mate: I
